name: Cs313e-netflix
body: Netflix Prize is one of five projects required for Professor Downing's CS313E class.  This project is a remake of Netflix's 2009 contest solely made for the class, but all rules and guidelines are kept the same.  The project is written in Python.  To read more about the rules and guidelines, click [here](http://www.netflixprize.com/rules).
